```
Rows: 30
Columns: 3
$ drug <fct> A, A, A, A, A, A, A, A, A, A, D, D, D, D, D, D, D, D, D, D, F, F,…
$ pre  <dbl> 11, 8, 5, 14, 19, 6, 10, 6, 11, 3, 6, 6, 7, 8, 18, 8, 19, 8, 5, 1…
$ post <dbl> 6, 0, 2, 8, 11, 4, 13, 1, 8, 0, 0, 2, 3, 1, 18, 4, 14, 9, 1, 9, 1…
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
df_sas %>% summary()
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
