```


:::
:::



## The Model



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
model_ancova <- lm(post ~ drug + pre, data = df_sas)
model_glance <- model_ancova %>% glance()
model_tidy   <- model_ancova %>% tidy()
model_glance %>% gt()
```

